  "notes": "Anarch Status- Bold, Spirited, Daring, Fearless*2, Honorable, Trusted, Respected, Trustworthy.\n\n11,329,000.00- Earnings from the Auction/Fundraiser for Guiding Light Foundation.\n\n$2,000,000\n\nWarded Dagger (**?)\n\nLanguages: Japanese, Gaelic, Latin, German, Russian, Italian, Turkish, Mongolian, Irish, Scottish, Ancient Babylonian\n\nBusinesses:\n1. The Artistic Tattoo Parlor (Chain of tattoo parlors)\n2. HTC (piercing equipment and now getting back into surgical tools where HTC started)\n3. Caines CamelBack Sporting goods and safe Co. (has safes, bows, guns, rifles etc.)\n4. The Beacon Homeless shelter (it was set up during the first brujah war)\n5. Ice Age Cold Storage Facility in North west Phoenix (built during the first brujah war)\n6. The Chute Male spa (Gay Bath house on Indian School)\n7. The Tool Shed resort (Gay Bath House in Apache Junction near Crimson and Southern)\n8. The Castle Boutique on Camelback\n9. The Shadows Apartment complex (30 single level units)\n\nHavens:\n1. Under terminal 3 of Scottsdale airport\n2. Tiger slash\n3. Phoenix Zoo\n4. His sporting good store\n5. His cold storage facility\n6. And his various locations of his tattoo parlors\n7. Both bath houses\n8. Hollowed out Cavern in side of Camel Back mountain\n\nGained Disfigured Flaw from Agg Damage due to Sunlight.\n\nMentor to Khrystiana Marovich\n\n250,000,000 in Silver Ingots\n\nRoad of Chivalry - Rating Minimum wrongdoing for a conviction roll:\n10 Failing to assist mortals in need.\n9 Treating a peer with disrespect.\n8 Placing personal desire above duty.\n7 Breaking your word to a clanmate or peer.\n6 Failing to assist clanmates or peers in need.\n5 Striking an unarmed opponent.\n4 Failing to provide hospitality to another Cainite.\n3 Treating a superior with disrespect.\n2 Breaking your word to your lord or prince.\n1 Breaking a sacred oath.\n\nWay of Fire (Koldunic Sorcery) - See detailed notes in character file.\n\nST NOTES: Gained Lore Faerie (Free via RP), Lore Umbra (Free Via DT and RP)\n\nMajor Pact signed - gained Ancient Babylonian language, Unbondable merit, Nature changed to Survivor, knowledge of Way of Fire and various Lores.\n\nAll Local Gangrel Prestige removed by Randall Alpha of AZ 4/12/03",
  "equipment": "Flame Thrower (+0, 2 Aggravated, Heavy, Hot), Flame Thrower Gloves (2), Warded Dagger (**?)",
